Title: Plasson Valves 9056 bib tap with double check valve 1/2"
Description: Designed for external installation, the Plasson 9056 bib tap with 1/2" BSP x hose union connections provides water for use in infrastructure, agriculture or horticulture applications. Offering total control over water flow, this tap is designed with a threaded check valve which releases pressure to the preferred level while preventing backflow, minimising the risk of contamination in sensitive settings.
